83
00:07:26,900 --> 00:07:28,560
only the story of your stupid…

84
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,630
the story

85
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:33,920
of your cute

86
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,750
little star

87
00:07:36,050 --> 00:07:37,159
can make it up to me.

88
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,000
