89
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,430
There's a custom in Eastern Country.

90
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:09,390
At the coming-of-age ceremony at 18,

91
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:11,720
mothers give their children a small gift.

92
